<strong>WORKS CITED</strong>
<br><br>
Add a &#8216;Works Cited&#8217; entry at the end of your essay citing all sources used in the body of your writing.
<br><br>
<strong>Format</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	Name of corporate Author. <em>Title</em>. Publisher, year.  
</blockquote>
<br>
<strong>Example</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	<span class="hover" title="Name of Corporate Author">Institute of Chartered Accountants in Australia.</span> 
	<span class="hover" title="Title"><em>AASB Standards for 2005: Equivalents to IFRSs as at August 2004</em></span>.
	<span class="hover" title="Publisher">Pearson Education</span>,
	<span class="hover" title="Year">2004</span>.
</blockquote>
<br>
